    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a collector-grade example that looks and drives as if it just left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining a deep, mirror-like finish with no scratches, dents, or chips to be found. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather upholstery, dashboard, and carpets showing zero signs of wear or aging. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history, ensuring a smooth and reliable driving experience for the next owner.",
