    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you should expect some minor oil seepage and a suspension that feels a bit loose over bumps. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some fading on the clear coat, while the interior shows moderate wear on the driver's seat and carpet. It is a solid, honest car that is ready for the road today but will eventually benefit from some mechanical and cosmetic refreshing.",
