    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable companion for your daily adventures? This car is in fair condition and ready for a new home! It shows some honest signs of its journey so far, with a few cosmetic imperfections, but it remains a solid and dependable choice for anyone needing a functional ride. It's been well-maintained mechanically and is eager to hit the road with its next owner!",
