    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car! It\u2019s been such a fantastic ride for me and has never let me down. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-cared for\u2014perfect for your daily commute or fun weekend getaways. It runs smoothly and looks sharp, though it has just a bit of that 'lived-in' character you'd expect from a car that's actually been enjoyed. I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
